    "name": "Text (Maundy Thursday)",
    "liturgy_name": "Maundy Thursday",
    "liturgy_slug": "maundy_thursday_anglican",
    "kind": "prayer-body",
    "body_text": "Peace is my last gift to you, my own peace I now leave with you; peace which the world cannot give, I give to you. I give you a new commandment: Love one another as I have loved you. Peace is my last gift to you, my own peace I now leave with you; peace which the world cannot give, I give to you. By this shall the world know that you are my disciples: That you have love for one another.",
